text: Sugao Kambe (born 2 August 1961) is a former Japanese football player. Kambe started to coach JEF United Ichihara Chiba in October, 2011. ==References== *Kambe to coach Northern Mariana Islands ==Other websites== *Sugao Kambe at FIFA.com Category:1961 births Category:Living people Category:Footballers from Shizuoka Prefecture
